Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Brieven Rubens an Gevaerts 15 Sept. 1629. Vollständig" addressed (inside) to "Herrn Prof. G. Evers Hans (?) Altwies über Kaltbrunn St. Gallen Schweitz" and dated 19.09.1966

- Transcription (in german) of a letter from Rubens to Gevaerts
- Photo of the original letter
